      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; analyst qualification and simulation execution checklist serve as proxy controls.",
      "rationale": "Use error is not required to be formally assessed at MRL 2. Analyst qualifications (minimum 5 years CFD experience in cardiovascular devices) and a documented simulation execution checklist (Form CFD-EXEC-03) are in place as procedural controls. This factor is not-assessed per the MRL 2 scoping decision."
