      "rationale": "Formal model-form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2. The turbulence model sensitivity study (SST k-omega vs. realizable k-epsilon) showed less than 6% variation in RH across operating points, providing qualitative confidence in model-form robustness. This factor is not-assessed per the MRL 2 scoping decision."
    },
    {
