      "rationale": "Formal model input uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2. Blood viscosity and density were sourced from published literature (Merrill et al.) with stated uncertainty ranges. Power-law hemolysis model constants (C, α, β) were taken from the Giersiepen correlation with acknowledged parametric uncertainty. This factor is not-assessed per the MRL 2 scoping decision."
    },
